{"tid":1991394,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［全民脫支］想獨立建國先要文化切割？","createTime":"2020-04-27T11:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T11:57:28.000Z","uid":61577,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a01174f372c35477d600633643f6fd23f0a4f9ad","tid":1991394,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:37:45.000Z","msg":"就到五四運動，諗起個有趣問題<br />\n<br />\n文化核心（天人合一，大一統）塑造生活習慣<br />\n咁用逆向思維，改變生活習慣係咪就可以改變文化核心，從而將支那基因盡量洗走？<br />\n例如語言上盡量用英文溝通（我英文差所以出唔到post)飲食貼近西餐，倫理上強調個人主義（養兒防老用孝道係咪要放棄？）娛樂上聽英文歌睇西片等等<br />\n大部分人用西式文化生活係咪就可以脫支？<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768f4bd654d804ff8bdeae983f6dd7b14142c4af","tid":1991394,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae6f234cffe7273b2243693bd11b3ea573af846","tid":1991394,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"768f4bd654d804ff8bdeae983f6dd7b14142c4af","tid":1991394,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:47:44.000Z","msg":"hyperjj<br />\ncall me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d743eb2cf206c584569c37bb9be0656cc7d59a","tid":1991394,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:52:59.000Z","msg":"除非你發明一種新語言<br />\n用英文都只係向西方靠攏"},{"pid":"6b70b24a536d569b6a2470895a574ef81550510d","tid":1991394,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d4d743eb2cf206c584569c37bb9be0656cc7d59a","tid":1991394,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:52:59.000Z","msg":"除非你發明一種新語言<br />\n用英文都只係向西方靠攏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"Anyway but Chinese"}]}